  "response": "The legal system combats money laundering through multiple strategies:\n\n1. Anti-Money Laundering (AML) Laws\n- Comprehensive legal frameworks\n- Mandatory reporting requirements\n- Financial transaction monitoring\n\n2. Investigative Techniques\n- Forensic accounting\n- Electronic transaction tracing\n- Collaboration between agencies\n- Advanced data analysis\n\n3. International Cooperation\n- Information sharing between countries\n- Extradition agreements\n- Coordinated enforcement efforts\n\n4. Prosecution Strategies\n- Targeting financial infrastructure\n- Seizing illicit assets\n- Imposing significant penalties\n- Prosecuting complex financial crimes\n\n5. Technological Tools\n- Advanced tracking software\n- Machine learning algorithms\n- Digital forensic techniques\n\n6. Financial Institution Compliance\n- Know Your Customer (KYC) regulations\n- Suspicious activity reporting\n- Internal control mechanisms\n\nThese approaches help disrupt sophisticated money laundering networks through comprehensive legal and technological strategies.",
